---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import HiwUpload from '../components/HiwUpload.astro';
import HiwCreate from '../components/HiwCreate.astro';
import HiwShare from '../components/HiwShare.astro';
---
<Base title="Shnappy — Client proofing made easy." active="home">
  <div class="layout__banner layout__banner--alpha">
    <div class="center center--1120">
      <div class="home-banner clearfix">
        <div class="home-banner__half">
          <div class="home-banner__headline">
            <h1 class="heading-1 text-white">Client proofing has never been easier.</h1>
            <h4 class="heading-subtitle text-white">Communicate with clients. Proof photos.</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="home-banner__cta">
            <a class="button button--48 button--white-stroke button--inline" href="/sign-up">Get started for free →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="home-banner__half">
          <div class="home-banner__screenshot"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="layout__section layout__section--grey">
    <div class="center center--1120">
      <div class="hiw-layout clearfix">
        <div class="hiw-layout__heading">
          <h2 class="heading-2 text-dark text-center">How Shnappy works</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw-layout__item">
          <div class="hiw-item">
            <div class="hiw-item__step">1</div>
            <div class="hiw-item__image"><HiwUpload /></div>
            <div class="hiw-item__title">Upload photos</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw-layout__item">
          <div class="hiw-item">
            <div class="hiw-item__step">2</div>
            <div class="hiw-item__image"><HiwCreate /></div>
            <div class="hiw-item__title">Create Galleries</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw-layout__item">
          <div class="hiw-item">
            <div class="hiw-item__step">3</div>
            <div class="hiw-item__image"><HiwShare /></div>
            <div class="hiw-item__title">Share with clients</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="layout__section layout__section--white">
    <div class="center center--1120">
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="row row--align-center">
          <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-6 col-sm-hide"><div class="placeholder-image"></div></div>
          <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
            <div class="website-example">
              <div class="website-example__heading"><h1 class="heading-2">Built for your clients, 100% mobile ready.</h1></div>
              <div class="website-example__content">
                <div class="typography">
                  <p>You've spent the time and energy creating awesome photos — they deserve to be shown off as the art they are.</p>
                  <p>Shnappy provides a quick and modern photo gallery portal that runs across all of your clients' devices — from mobile phones through to web-enabled TVs.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-sm-show"><div class="placeholder-image"></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hr"></div>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="row row--align-center">
          <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
            <div class="website-example">
              <div class="website-example__heading"><h1 class="heading-2">Export once, upload once.</h1></div>
              <div class="website-example__content">
                <div class="typography">
                  <p>Export your photos once in high quality and let Shnappy take care of creating thumbnails and applying your watermark for you, allowing you to focus on what matters — your clients.</p>
                  <p>Shnappy lets you choose where you want your photos to live — under your control in Dropbox or safely in Shnappy's cloud storage.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-6 col-sm-12"><div class="placeholder-image"></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hr"></div>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="row row--align-center">
          <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-6 col-sm-hide"><div class="placeholder-image"></div></div>
          <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
            <div class="website-example">
              <div class="website-example__heading"><h1 class="heading-2">See activity when it happens.<br />Communicate quickly. Build relationships.</h1></div>
              <div class="website-example__content">
                <div class="typography">
                  <p>Keeping the communication channels open during the delivery and proofing stage allows you to deliver results that your clients are super happy with.</p>
                  <p>Shnappy lets your clients comment on individual photos and notifies you instantly. No more awkward emails with file names!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-sm-show"><div class="placeholder-image"></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hr"></div>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="row row--align-center">
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
            <div class="website-example">
              <div class="website-example__title"><p>Professional Feature</p></div>
              <div class="website-example__heading"><h1 class="heading-2 text-blue">Attract new clients with your own portfolio site.</h1></div>
              <div class="website-example__content">
                <div class="typography">
                  <p>Build your own portfolio site by simply dragging photos into Dropbox. Attract new clients by showing off your best work.</p>
                  <p>Potential clients can learn all about your work and get in touch to book their next photo shoot.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="website-example__action"><a class="button button--48 button--blue" href="/examples">Learn more</a></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-6 col-sm-12"><div class="placeholder-image"></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</Base>
